    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant with factory-spec sequential twin turbochargers. This example retains its original Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and Torsen limited-slip differential. Every component, from the double-wishbone suspension to the four-piston magnesium alloy calipers, remains in impeccable condition. The chassis exhibits zero torsional fatigue, and the engine maintains factory-standard compression across all six cylinders. A true collector\u2019s piece with a pristine undercarriage and unmodified ECU.",
