      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. The wheels are pristine with no curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with near-total tread life remaining. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and taut, the carpets are spotless, and the dashboard is free of any sun-fading or wear. Every electronic feature and mechanical component operates with factory precision. The engine bay is detailed to a professional standard, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians using genuine OEM parts. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did on the day of its original delivery. Perfect for the collector or the enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
