    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-compression engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system to achieve a linear 8,000 RPM powerband. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory M-variable limited-slip differential with a 3.64 final drive ratio. This example is mechanically superlative: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing recall is documented as completed. The suspension retains its original geometry with refreshed bushings and Sachs dampers, ensuring the chassis remains as rigid and communicative as the day it left Regensburg. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a pristine interior reflect its meticulously preserved status.",
